Cell["\<\
Method -> \"Embedding\" ranks the line vertices by Euclidean proximity to the \
projection of coord(point) onto the affine line under the graph drawing.\
\>", "CodeText",ExpressionUUID->"525b440e-939f-44f2-8031-5ca1b8fe6f8d"],

